    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "上苍不绝薛后代",
        "吴奇",
        "四头目",
        "四将官",
        "四马甲",
        "英雄虎胆比天大",
        "薛义",
        "薛刚",
        "马赞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四将官、囚车、薛刚引薛义同上，囚车在前。〖一条龙〗。〖内喊声〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里人马呐喊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四将官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "强人挡道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "囚车打入松林。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二将官抬囚车、薛刚自上场门同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴奇、马赞、四喽兵、四头目、四马甲自上场门同上，撞阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，来的官兵，留下三千黄金，以作买路钱，放你过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，大胆的响马，你要买路钱，也要打听明白，或是客商孤单，便可行劫。我\n押解钦犯，上长安去的，哪有银钱与你？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，俺知道你是泗水关总兵，尽有金银去送奸臣。怎说没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是献功讨赏的，哪有什么金银？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既没有银钱，将钦犯留下作为赏头，转去拿些金银来取。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆强盗，吃你侯爷一枪，众将退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四将官自两边分下，薛义跑下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里走！\n（吴奇、马赞同追下。一对二杀打，同下。薛义上，前走，吴奇、马赞同追上。薛义倒地。四喽兵、四头目、\n四马甲自两边分上，同绑薛义。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众喽啰，先将这贼押回山寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四喽兵押薛义同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快将囚车内薛爵主请出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四头目、四马甲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、四马甲同下，四头目、四马甲随薛刚同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，多谢二位英雄搭救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭救来迟，爵主恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请爵主同上山寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可曾拿住薛义？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已押上山去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳二位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喽啰回山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四头目、四马甲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问二位高姓尊名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺吴奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马赞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么知道薛刚至此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前有李靖大仙言道，有泗水关总兵薛义负义忘恩，叫我等在此相救爵主，权避\n此山，后整唐皇天下。许我二人蟒袍玉带。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，感谢大仙恩德，又蒙二位搭救，俺薛刚何日答报？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我弟兄要与爵主结为异姓同胞，不知爵主意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承蒙搭救，又结昆仑，俺怎好高攀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。\n来，吩咐杀猪宰羊，准备香案伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承蒙不弃，只是我要往长安祭扫丘坟，要相烦同往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二人愿随三哥去祭坟台，回山齐集人马，杀上长安，与一门报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请三哥先吃一杯接风酒，然后再拜金兰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。三桌齐坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三哥请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问三哥，将薛义怎么发落？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐将他绑上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四头目、四马甲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四头目、四马甲绑薛义同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四头目、四马甲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛义当面！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀，贼子啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛刚打薛义。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "负义昧心将我害，\n尔是人面兽投胎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛刚打薛义。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乌纱紫袍是哪里来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不记得在长安卖与张天佑为奴，只因那奸贼看上你妻子花容，要她为妾。你\n妻子守节不从，将你送到法堂，五刑拷打，追比身价银两。你妻子杨氏街坊求\n乞。我一股仗义，与你完了身价，救你出监，认你同宗弟兄，又与你干此总兵。\n不思知恩报恩，反诓我进府，以酒迷我，拿住解京，贪图万户侯。不料天理\n昭昭，我命不该死，有人搭救。俺薛刚虽然烈性，待你却是恩厚，为何反要害\n我？俺是哪些待你不好，你讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我讲什么呢？这算我的错，只好请副香纸，叩一个头就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，贼子啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人心不足蛇心坏，\n螳螂捕蝉反受灾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀贼子啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "善恶昭彰救星来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "上苍不绝薛后代、吴奇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三哥，这等无义之人，还有什么理与他讲？将这贼碎尸万段就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理.\n喽啰将薛义剐了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四头目、四马甲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛义脱衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我冤仇如沧海，\n刀下将你碎尸骸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狼心贼子，待俺来看你心肝五脏，是怎么生长？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从前报我如犬马，\n如今设计将某拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "英雄虎胆比天大、吴奇、马赞",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好拿来下酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抛入松林赏乌鸦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛刚乱砍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
